= Navigation Tags

Provides basic navigation for your app. 

<r:nav /> outputs a navigation list like: 

  <div id="nav">
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/about/">About</a></li>
      <li>
        <a href="/blog/">Blog</a>
        <ul>
          <li class="current"><a href="/blog/2007/04/11/first-article-radiant-with-comments/">First Article-Radiant with Comments</a></li>

          <li><a href="/blog/2007/04/11/second-article/">Second Article</a></li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

